snippet.title: Box Knight - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Quest your way up the office tower, fight monstrous abstractions of your most toxic co-workers and bring good vibes back to the office. Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1678650/Box_Knight/

A funny, silly and irreverent action RPG roguelike. If The Office, Lord of The Rings and South Park had an angry baby. 

Website: https://playboxknight.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/boxknightgame
Discord: https://discord.gg/prQV6Y29PG
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wemadeathingstudios
